code: @Override protected synchronized AsyncProcessor chooseProcessor(AsyncProcessor[] processors, Exchange exchange) {     int counter = this.counter.     List<DistributionRatio> ratios = getRatios().     while (true) {         if (++counter >= ratios.size()) {             counter = 0.         }         DistributionRatio ratio = ratios.get(counter).         if (ratio.decrement()) {             this.counter = lastIndex = counter.             decrementSum().             return processors[counter].         }     } }
